<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="extension-n">extension <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪk'stenʃn/    美 /ɪk'stenʃn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>延伸；扩大；延长期：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a visa extension
延长签证</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The wire has an <strong>extension of</strong> 50 feet.
电线可伸长到50英尺。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>extension of</strong> the garden will take several weeks.
扩建花园需要几个星期。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The pub had an extension on Christmas Eve.
这家酒吧在圣诞前夜延长营业时间。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>扩建部分：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The city is building an <strong>extension to</strong> the subway line.
这座城市正在扩建地铁线路</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>电话分机；分机号码：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Extension 326, please!
请接326分机。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="by-extension">by extension</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[正式用法]再则</strong>  </p></div>